To-Do List App

CodSoft Frontend Development Internship – Task 2

This project was developed as Task 2 of my CodSoft Frontend Development Internship. It is a responsive To-Do List App that helps users organize and manage their daily tasks efficiently. The application is built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript with a simple, clean, and user-friendly interface.

✨ Features

- Add new tasks
- Edit existing tasks
- Delete completed or unwanted tasks
- Mark tasks as completed
- Responsive design for all devices
- Clean and intuitive user interface
- Easy-to-use task management

🛠️ Tech Stack

- HTML5
- CSS3
- JavaScript
